        "\n",
        "Observed: 'B' - \\['B', 'B'\\], p(B) = 1.0, ways to produce = 2 - \\['B', 'W'\\], p(B) = 0.5, ways to produce = 1 - \\['W', 'W'\\], p(B) = 0.0, ways to produce = 0\n",
